訴求缺一不可"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:28:15.000Z","msg":"屌你個冷氣軍師都係on9冇實戰經驗 <br />\n冇人叫你一定要行到終點<br />\n行一半唔通犯法咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行入去正on9<br />\n講完 <br />\n洗撚分析<br />\n觀塘大撚把街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7a8162ac427dc22406559bc0bd58cde9bd0c99","tid":1499470,"uid":232237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba546d3bf5a3b19af42db3e78198a98a6a7d831b","tid":1499470,"uid":10684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:26:17.000Z","msg":"簡單啲講 百里香隔離"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:28:35.000Z","msg":"執撚柒左啦"},{"pid":"71b088f386d321bbd7fb823925af520e29cca1b4","tid":1499470,"uid":8081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:28:37.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qP34CSq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqP34CSq.jpg&h=8ef85dee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7a874083a4046d44a5943190609c4242fe347ea","tid":1499470,"uid":249722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:28:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"850313b0ac37837b329c481a21472c97b6560231","tid":1499470,"uid":10684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e7a8162ac427dc22406559bc0bd58cde9bd0c99","tid":1499470,"uid":232237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba546d3bf5a3b19af42db3e78198a98a6a7d831b","tid":1499470,"uid":10684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:26:17.000Z","msg":"簡單啲講 百里香隔離"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:28:35.000Z","msg":"執撚柒左啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:30:36.000Z","msg":"改咗名BBQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過唔緊要 知係邊就得"},{"pid":"243ff0b4b17f2c6ee89c326d336ba59b2f777462","tid":1499470,"uid":161322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:30:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c98ac6ff33552bb7b05d6e690143a791cf1f7935","tid":1499470