實戰經驗 <br />\n冇人叫你一定要行到終點<br />\n行一半唔通犯法咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行入去正on9<br />\n講完 <br />\n洗撚分析<br />\n觀塘大撚把街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:42:17.000Z","msg":"第一，你有冇睇遊行路線? 附近邊到會經過觀塘街坊居住地? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />遊行路線附近全部都係工廈商廈同酒店，九龍灣，牛頭角同觀塘街坊全部都係住觀塘道左邊，但遊行路線係住觀塘道右邊<br />\n<br />\n講句難聽D，POPO係遊行起點同終點放足煙花都冇咩影響，附近根本冇居民又冇老人院，有咩驚? 最多驚手震射咗粒TG落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一，觀塘街坊會幫手，一睇就知你唔係住呢區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />觀塘好多廢老，新移民，唔落樓打埋你一份算偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08dadd32b56af22a65dcaa2a04e35d4407a2e634","tid":1499470,"uid":161322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:42:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24f1c25890f92321a6b560110db41db262662ab2","tid":1499470,"uid":281243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aef98be96d61db114714ae32d3c3b317f208063","tid":1499470,"uid":281243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:19:38.000Z","msg":"先講個結論，九龍灣零碳做終點，對於我地撤退(不論前線或係和理非)都十分不利，因為好容易會被POPO包圍。<br />\n先大概分析九龍灣工業區地形<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/azh5mYz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fazh5mYz.png&h=0941c026&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n1) 零碳天地位於工業區正中位置，附近全部都係工業同商業大廈，POPO今次好快就出咗不反對通知，呢D工廈同商廈應該一早收到通知星期六會落閘閂門，加上呢區道路窄，所以第1) 大廈高， TG唔容易被風吹散，第2) 如果入夜出防暴，冇咩地方可以躲藏，附近工廈閂哂門，好彩既有megabox可以入一入<br />\n<br />\n2) <span style=\"color: red;\">紅色圈</span>分別係<strong>輔助警察總部</strong> 同<strong>牛頭角分區警署</strong>(東九龍行動基地)，一個終點附近已經有兩個狗處，地方大，人手同車輛安排都自然可以放多D，勇武手足要注意有機會出現敵眾我寡(不論在明或在暗)，以自身安全同不被捕為優先考慮!!!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>撤退分析</em></strong><br />\n九龍灣工業區的入面交通企實唔方便，平日得小巴同巴士會穿過工業區，但聽日應該有機會會改道，出發前要注意。<br />\n<br />\n而附近最四通八達既只係得九龍灣地鐵同樓下既巴士站(<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍色圈</span>)，呢個位基本上係全香港都可以去到，但正正因為係最方便，所以如果一封地鐵或者有POPO Mon 住地鐵同巴士站，佢地就可以隨便捉人查身份證，甚至拘捕。建議如果有腳骨力，可以向上行經啟業(附近有巴士站/再行上D去彩虹)，或者向下去觀塘道休憩處既巴士站，再行落D有牛頭角地鐵站。<br />\n而啟德個邊，個人唔建議去，一方面遠，另外果到全部都係地盤，零交通可言，根本係個死城。<br />\n<br />\n結論:<br />\n小弟住九龍灣已經十年，希望儘下綿力，幫到幾多就係幾多。個人認為係零碳天地(九龍灣工業區)附近同POPO搏火，係唔值得(非割席，單純個人意見)，因為真係九龍灣既地型好容易會俾人反包圍，最多撚完狗就好be water，唔好戀戰。<br />\n<br />\n#以上都係以終點零碳天地作分析，如果想番去到駿業街遊樂場，可以考慮1. 觀塘地鐵 2. 觀塘碼頭巴士總站 3. 觀塘碼頭去北角<br />\n#小弟第一次出post，各位多多指教<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:47:10.000Z","msg":"補多兩張圖<br />\n牛頭角分區警署<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ysu3Twt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fysu3Twt.png&h=6a622c34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港輔助警察總部 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ubspCYc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FubspCYc.png&h=70aee3da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de00b79bc15532cc10053dccb8f224d95a41df45","tid":1499470,"uid":276388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:49:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71c0e07c6a6a54a2b6365c581d583e01642f2d7b","tid":1499470,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:54:28.000Z","msg":"行完參觀下零碳就行circle k對住果條街返德福走人啦，或者遊下megabox<br />\n最多去港鐵總部屌下高層，但星期六應該冇人返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個地方冇咩有價值目標，行完好閃水"},{"pid":"707ecda0bdd6b31d76e33eb84ba023634883e2cb","tid":1499470,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db91090080f56da326382c6c2bfc9630c059afe9","tid":1499470,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:01:12.000Z","msg":"大力推行動post呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b1db4401d7ec8eb0e3062191c0722f4c73a5f2","tid":1499470,"uid":240648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:02:41.000Z","msg":"如果行觀塘道出彩虹係咪要過行人隧道"},{"pid":"2a50e48ad706037a24404c6fda061203658cac72","tid":1499470,"uid":109047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:04:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee419632dd3a6c597f33fe2d1e99606690676fad","tid":1499470,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:06:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3635271d3ce92d0dd44d9b1fcb8f4577d7428ee8","tid":1499470,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:07:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49ca2465e4e3b6c4288399ef441719abdf932464","tid":1499470,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:07:24.000Z","msg":"德福散水得唔得"},{"pid":"9ec0e62a1f60708d9eb7bdf8ab95eb19abc3ae11","tid":1499470,"uid":155027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:10:11.000Z","msg":"觀塘見"},{"pid":"4296bfd71dea5843930ae95c45c283fcaf9ac950","tid":1499470,"uid":59390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:12:56.000Z","msg":"824 觀塘見！"},{"pid":"1dea78964f7f9d2b701a02d7fc12d5a8a8088abe","tid":1499470,"uid":209464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:14:37.000Z","msg":"be water, 行完走，唔好久留。個位除咗megabox外就係全商業同工廠區，一封就冇車走，除非向後出由牛頭角出觀塘道，否則向左係大馬路，條路仲要係入舊機隧，向前係副狗總部，向右係東九龍行動基地，去德福二期要經過基地，偉業街上德福花園得頭尾兩條窄到死嘅天橋，基本上成個位置同地型係輸晒。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 沿途好多商業大厦出晒通告，中午開始鎖玻璃門，要由側門過保安出職員證先入得"},{"pid":"f77fb0d1caf6f8839a13adeb5da9aea2c2ba8ae9","tid":1499470,"uid":34065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b74e79f741362e7052a4824f3d81f427031b40f","tid":1499470,"uid":27456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:18:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df248efa83de005299b0dae159c422e2319e85bc","tid":1499470,"uid":233014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"46f1a3cd4b2ce2ed3473b3e57d69bd80f333458d","tid":1499470,"uid":281243,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d698ce0806a4864e1a6fecb885255513a5af9455","tid":1499470,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"8aef98be96d61db114714ae32d3c3b317f208063","tid":1499470,"uid":281243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:19:38.000Z","msg":"先講個結論，九龍灣零碳做終點，對於我地撤退(不論前線或係和理非)都十分不利，因為好容易會被POPO包圍。<br />\n先大概分析九龍灣工業區地形<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/azh5mYz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fazh5mYz.png&h=0941c026&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n1) 零碳天地位於工業區正中位置，附近全部都係工業同商業大廈，POPO今次好快就出咗不反對通知，呢D工廈同商廈應該一早收到通知星期六會落閘閂門，加上呢區道路窄，所以第1) 大廈高， TG唔容易被風吹散，第2) 如果入夜出防暴，冇咩地方可以躲藏，附近工廈閂哂門，好彩既有megabox可以入一入<br />\n<br />\n2) <span style=\"color: red;\">紅色圈</span>分別係<strong>輔助警察總部</strong> 同<strong>牛頭角分區警署</strong>(東九龍行動基地)，一個終點附近已經有兩個狗處，地方大，人手同車輛安排都自然可以放多D，勇武手足要注意有機會出現敵眾我寡(不論在明或在暗)，以自身安全同不被捕為優先考慮!!!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>撤退分析</em></strong><br />\n九龍灣工業區的入面交通企實唔方便，平日得小巴同巴士會穿過工業區，但聽日應該有機會會改道，出發前要注意。<br />\n<br />\n而附近最四通八達既只係得九龍灣地鐵同樓下既巴士站(<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍色圈</span>)，呢個位基本上係全香港都可以去到，但正正因為係最方便，所以如果一封地鐵或者有POPO Mon 住地鐵同巴士站，佢地就可以隨便捉人查身份證，甚至拘捕。建議如果有腳骨力，可以向上行經啟業(附近有巴士站/再行上D去彩虹)，或者向下去觀塘道休憩處既巴士站，再行落D有牛頭角地鐵站。<br />\n而啟德個邊，個人唔建議去，一方面遠，另外果到全部都係地盤，零交通可言，根本係個死城。<br />\n<br />\n結論:<br />\n小弟住九龍灣已經十年，希望儘下綿力，幫到幾多就係幾多。個人認為係零碳天地(九龍灣工業區)附近同POPO搏火，係唔值得(非割席，單純個人意見)，因為真係九龍灣既地型好容易會俾人反包圍，最多撚完狗就好be water，唔好戀戰。<br />\n<br />\n#以上都係以終點零碳天地作分析，如果想番去到駿業街遊樂場，可以考慮1. 觀塘地鐵 2. 觀塘碼頭巴士總站 3. 觀塘碼頭去北角<br />\n#小弟第一次出post，各位多多指教<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:28:15.000Z","msg":"屌你個冷氣軍師都係on9冇實戰經驗 <br />\n冇人叫你一定要行到終點<br />\n行一半唔通犯法咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行入去正on9<br />\n講完 <br />\n洗撚分析<br />\n觀塘大撚把街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:42:17.000Z","msg":"第一，你有冇睇遊行路線? 附近邊到會經過觀塘街坊居住地? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />遊行路線附近全部都係工廈商廈同酒店，九龍灣，牛頭角同觀塘街坊全部都係住觀塘道左邊，但遊行路線係住觀塘道右邊<br />\n<br />\n講句難聽D，POPO係遊行起點同終點放足煙花都冇咩影響，附近根本冇居民又冇老人院，有咩驚? 最多驚手震射咗粒TG落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一，觀塘街坊會幫手，一睇就知你唔係住呢區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />觀塘好多廢老，新移民，唔落樓打埋你一份算偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:21:11.000Z","msg":"認真勁撚多廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本上唔洗諗住有人幫手<br />\n遊行途中走嚟屌你就有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屋企下面個公告板有議員貼警察暴力行李都有撕紙狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有平時馬路啲議員橫副 寫住林奠下台 比廢老畫到花晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28bffd81ac136ccfa131a2804eba7c883c6db76d","tid":1499470,"uid":34065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2ed57088e56e0c68a6636989de6e99acd8ddb0","tid":1499470,"uid":211974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:21:43.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95dbae58eeab73094f2d01c3e7bab6476ddb775b","tid":1499470,"uid":64283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:23:50.000Z","msg":"手足真係不宜戀戰白送頭<br />\n最多參觀下d燈柱好啦<br />\n<br />\n住左觀塘3x年<br />\n非常同意樓主分析"},{"pid":"bdbe6e26fef2d03b5d87a054a0d13a314e5cc286","tid":1499470,"uid":34065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:27:05.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4061d852db2c4659e702d16cda0c1166d7b71cc3","tid":1499470,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe49f72bab2353d8ba4f7847f8c8b4bf383f6952","tid":1499470,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:30:54.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"96101c27cf6ec19c3ae27f3e56e3a5189d9e9855","tid":1499470,"uid":171802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:36:21.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62579baa9afa4c33548c1834d16f029539b9000","tid":1499470,"uid":45259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:43:08.000Z","msg":"重有機會用埋下面啟德個消防局<br />\n<br />\n利申 <br />\n啱啱google map"},{"pid":"3ea2490f0a1f4d7734f89b448094471bc256aca3","tid":1499470,"uid":14543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:44:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7b484f12a70ec03f606015eaab07ebf288d8408","tid":1499470,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49ca2465e4e3b6c4288399ef441719abdf932464","tid":1499470,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:07:24.000Z","msg":"德福散水得唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:47:47.000Z","msg":"要睇偉業街有冇狗車<br />\n牛頭角狗屋一出車<br />\n轉個彎就到<br />\n而且佢批得不反對通知書<br />\n好大機會泊滿晒狗車"},{"pid":"f12ec999447ade05ab46cfbdab0beb6294a292a0","tid":1499470,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:49:37.000Z","msg":"九展EMAX出啟福道有巴士站<br />\n如果狗真係咬人，可以匿入九展<br />\n甚至換衫買飛睇場戲"},{"pid":"bb2275cf58f9bea6ba10a9ad01c1b153271853fa","tid":1499470,"uid":110519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:51:12.000Z","msg":"海濱長廊路闊 岩一大班人跑步<br />\n西行紅磡 東行藍田"},{"pid":"7cd509e4f6dd8ed1ecc0e5d92a990805540d43a9","tid":1499470,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:52:27.000Z","msg":"🤔"},{"pid":"eed5c999e4fdf90d92b9bf2efc57308c252f3b13","tid":1499470,"uid":13780,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:53:01.000Z","msg":"借位～～～<br />\n<br />\n最近見到大家一味發夢去太古站、葵芳站、元朗站靜坐、示威、表達訴求，目的係為左要港鐵正視乘客同員工安全，但係大家有冇諗過，你地夢中只係圍緊一班港鐵最前線既員工，係果度最大咪只係站長？佢可以代表港鐵講乜野？佢可以代港鐵道歉？佢可以影響港鐵乜野決定？你地咁樣只會令每一個基層前線員工受罪，我覺得錯既唔係基層，係果班坐係高高在上既管理層，我覺得佢地而家每日淨係坐緊係office食緊花生，恥笑緊我地香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2149692f9f8ada87746ab03b8b77ffd9b71d48","tid":1499470,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:54:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e7517f23b53909a81ecec136e341f4a4ec0aa26","tid":1499470,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb2275cf58f9bea6ba10a9ad01c1b153271853fa","tid":1499470,"uid":110519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:51:12.000Z","msg":"海濱長廊路闊 岩一大班人跑步<br />\n西行紅磡 東行藍田"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:56:42.000Z","msg":"你意思係經啟德消防局返觀塘海濱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6498e61848c94664c774e73b23b32eb833dbc51","tid":1499470,"uid":29088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:59:54.000Z","msg":"光復香港時代革命"},{"pid":"d9bada7ee8b7654ebf1b847c2d6e6b51b5c7a7ad","tid":1499470,"uid":110519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e7517f23b53909a81ecec136e341f4a4ec0aa26","tid":1499470,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb2275cf58f9bea6ba10a9ad01c1b153271853fa","tid":1499470,"uid":110519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:51:12.000Z","msg":"海濱長廊路闊 岩一大班人跑步<br />\n西行紅磡 東行藍田"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:56:42.000Z","msg":"你意思係經啟德消防局返觀塘海濱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T19:09:21.000Z","msg":"以零炭天地為起點 <br />\n直接向海邊跑就係海濱長廊<br />\n<br />\n上網搵左兩張d人嘅練跑路線圖比大家參考<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/auFiHQ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FauFiHQ3.jpg&h=f476e942&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有條小路可以跑入遊輪碼頭觀光<br />\n唔觀光繼續向西跑就係土瓜灣 可以跑到去紅磡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H812p4p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH812p4p.jpg&h=ac6a6e3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東行就係落番觀塘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔轉上山 一直向東行就係麗港城/藍田<br />\n跑到攰咪坐巴士走"},{"pid":"b66add872c13f272598b5885cfbd522012e382b8","tid":1499470,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T19:45:23.000Z","msg":"824kt"},{"pid":"cbc90c28df49a92b719552a5c7fca97494c54356","tid":1499470,"uid":310355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T19:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d4045697b1632b09c6f6f5465b60a4b19b734b","tid":1499470,"uid":34065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T20:05:32.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baed2724b11c5ac01b4eac357a53b1e6692e5d51","tid":1499470,"uid":86753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T20:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b9ed0e8ec1c77362508cc03ba29230181f3ab3","tid":1499470,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T20:19:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c41740f4f47fbee265aa3f5cce491b80ca43810","tid":1499470,"uid":308450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T20:30:15.000Z","msg":"Megabox有shuttle bus 落返德福<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者入megabox行兩轉又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪放假都唔比人行街先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d18b2135b26ec401ed2ba8ea90e1c48b2c19705c","tid":1499470,"uid":106756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T22:46:17.000Z","msg":"終點位根本無險可守，牛頭角警署+輔警總部兩邊包抄就已經可以，如果再派人係德福黃金大道個位截查，基本上就封曬可以走既路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次沿遊行路線要離開既話，都最少要行十分鐘先到最近既港鐵站，加上係呢個時期佢都批得不反對，就一定係有信心可以輕易清到場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7efcf45e9c0dee2e60d9f4364813e533e7383b66","tid":1499470,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T23:01:18.000Z","msg":"光復香港時代革命"},{"pid":"17ccc5b63b8b79300f2c7f33b38df306988b2aa0","tid":1499470,"uid":87598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T23:35:33.000Z","msg":"提提大家，常悅道係佈滿智能燈柱。 請小心行事"},{"pid":"34beb05ed22a506ebea21e6ff5efc87b543c548a","tid":1499470,"uid":20262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71c0e07c6a6a54a2b6365c581d583e01642f2d7b","tid":1499470,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:54:28.000Z","msg":"行完參觀下零碳就行circle k對住果條街返德福走人啦，或者遊下megabox<br />\n最多去港鐵總部屌下高層，但星期六應該冇人返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個地方冇咩有價值目標，行完好閃水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T23:35:39.000Z","msg":"如果德福入防暴，或鎖站，<br />\n大條道理搞光復港鐵"},{"pid":"1b70f6141a3bba3a32221d29b5c0caa27fb09492","tid":1499470,"uid":281822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dea78964f7f9d2b701a02d7fc12d5a8a8088abe","tid":1499470,"uid":209464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:14:37.000Z","msg":"be water, 行完走，唔好久留。個位除咗megabox外就係全商業同工廠區，一封就冇車走，除非向後出由牛頭角出觀塘道，否則向左係大馬路，條路仲要係入舊機隧，向前係副狗總部，向右係東九龍行動基地，去德福二期要經過基地，偉業街上德福花園得頭尾兩條窄到死嘅天橋，基本上成個位置同地型係輸晒。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 沿途好多商業大厦出晒通告，中午開始鎖玻璃門，要由側門過保安出職員證先入得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T00:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7437ad92cd22e624314e7d3e44c0f6dc05f8b84","tid":1499470,"uid":281822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71c0e07c6a6a54a2b6365c581d583e01642f2d7b","tid":1499470,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:54:28.000Z","msg":"行完參觀下零碳就行circle k對住果條街返德福走人啦，或者遊下megabox<br />\n最多去港鐵總部屌下高層，但星期六應該冇人返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個地方冇咩有價值目標，行完好閃水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T00:23:45.000Z","msg":"CircleK成條街都智能燈柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd710a8a6e42c90717d0c7aa705e3024a873084f","tid":1499470,"uid":281105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T00:27:44.000Z","msg":"想搞義載，但點避車牌自動識別"},{"pid":"1a95b756beb96b61a3dc3532cdc27a5a5eaaca55","tid":1499470,"uid":278667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T00:54:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vFjb4NK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvFjb4NK.jpg&h=93198da1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q0BNC7K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ0BNC7K.jpg&h=fb8fa799&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ff0bbdfd0a5ec31ad7a454f40f09d2342615b95","tid":1499470,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:01:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n女義士被凌辱<br />\n新屋嶺集中營<br />\n五大訴求全無<br />\n爆眼護士之仇<br />\n元朗警黑合作<br />\n航空業大清算<br />\n被捕者七百餘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乜仇都未報到，唔好擺低你既憤怒！<br />\n我地絕對唔可以習慣，手足們繼續上街抗爭<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">８２４上午和你塞，下午觀塘遊行<br />\n８２５荃葵青大遊行</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uwUfM2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuwUfM2a.jpg&h=978ea62a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee69fdab9da558863819a91a4d30395d63c814e6","tid":1499470,"uid":80395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:25:13.000Z","msg":"如果佢要搞大，megabox 同九展係封硬，worst case係佢封埋過德福條橋。<br />\n<br />\n個遊行係有不反對通知書，所以要搞多數都只會係終點附近搞你，所以要諗路線，係要諗如常係唔用橋既狀態去到德福或者淘大果邊。<br />\n<br />\n最基本必要時先搞掂彩虹道先。"},{"pid":"8e339b5b48da7b2e1d23a924e5145442a80d86a3","tid":1499470,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:44:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"103d26f61d313c1243e12b2e960d1e00ae3b8325","tid":1499470,"uid":299261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:48:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18e1b82b2d48f697da08a03be34bb7daecb92ec7","tid":1499470,"uid":91230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:01:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b09cedff2fccef2bf5ea3d8107171016164e043e","tid":1499470,"uid":136662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6e9938aefa0c6d24ffbba503692ecfe82215e8","tid":1499470,"uid":124245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:09:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2727698d22078a05de3027eec1e4e511efa1823","tid":1499470,"uid":255222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:14:40.000Z","msg":"推"}]}